title: FrAdd New Levels
target: FrFactor variables to add new levels to
label1: FrAdd new levels to one or more factor variable(s). Save results to existing variables or create new variables by specifying a prefix/suffix. New variables will be created with the prefix/suffix appended to existing names.
newLevels: FrEnter new levels enclosed in quotes and separated by a comma for e.g. "level1","level2","level3
label2: FrSave new levels to new variable(s) or overwrite existing variable(s)
rd3: FrSpecify a suffix (A new variable will be created with the suffix)
rd2: Specify a prefix (A new variable will be created with the prefix)
